1
00:00:48,759 --> 00:00:49,280
Later,

2
00:00:49,399 --> 00:00:50,560
Xu Mengxi stepped up

3
00:00:51,240 --> 00:00:52,119
and claimed to the media

4
00:00:52,240 --> 00:00:53,079
that he was Wei'an.

5
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:55,000
Xu Mengxi?

6
00:00:55,240 --> 00:00:55,520
Yeah.

7
00:00:55,799 --> 00:00:56,479
Xu Mengxi?

8
00:00:59,119 --> 00:01:00,399
You don't know Xu Mengxi?

9
00:01:01,799 --> 00:01:03,759
How did you get to be Mr Xu's assistant?

10
00:01:05,599 --> 00:01:07,040
Oh, Xu Mengxi

11
00:01:07,239 --> 00:01:08,959
is my idol, my hero,

12
00:01:09,159 --> 00:01:10,799
the unbeatable in the online fiction world,

13
00:01:10,799 --> 00:01:12,000
the pinnacle of my admiration.

14
00:01:13,959 --> 00:01:14,439
Well,

15
00:01:14,760 --> 00:01:15,640
anyway,

16
00:01:15,840 --> 00:01:17,040
he suddenly claimed

17
00:01:17,159 --> 00:01:18,319
that Wei'an was his new pen name.

18
00:01:18,640 --> 00:01:20,280
He apologized to his fans, saying that

19
00:01:20,760 --> 00:01:22,000
he didn't expect Galaxy Chronicle

20
00:01:22,200 --> 00:01:23,400
to cause such a big stir.

21
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:24,680
And he claimed

22
00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:27,000
he would never use the pen name Wei'an again.

23
00:01:27,719 --> 00:01:29,719
That incident gradually subsided.

24
00:01:31,959 --> 00:01:32,480
Then,

25
00:01:32,799 --> 00:01:33,719
in that case,

26
00:01:35,359 --> 00:01:36,799
where is he now?

27
00:01:36,799 --> 00:01:37,680
What are you talking about?

28
00:01:38,079 --> 00:01:39,599
I'm a quality fan.

29
00:01:39,719 --> 00:01:40,560
Following someone's schedule

30
00:01:40,959 --> 00:01:42,480
is what stalkers do.

31
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:44,599
Xu Mengxi.

32
00:01:44,599 --> 00:01:46,200
He only lives in my heart.

33
00:01:47,400 --> 00:01:47,840
Ah.

34
00:01:51,239 --> 00:01:51,959
But

35
00:01:51,959 --> 00:01:53,680
I do have exclusive information.

36
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:54,680
Rumor has it

37
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:56,319
that Xu Mengxi and Mr. Xu

38
00:01:56,799 --> 00:01:57,359
have a deep relationship.

39
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,159
Are they...

40
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:00,239
Brother,

41
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:15,960
do you know Wei'an?

42
00:02:21,719 --> 00:02:22,280
No.

43
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:28,120
You're lying.

44
00:02:49,159 --> 00:02:49,639
You...

45
00:02:49,759 --> 00:02:50,680
Are you okay?

46
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:58,360
I've been in the army for years.

47
00:02:58,759 --> 00:02:59,879
I can easily

48
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:01,159
treat minor wounds.

49
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:02,080
Ah.

50
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:06,199
It's done.

51
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:09,960
Why are you crying?

52
00:03:12,039 --> 00:03:13,560
I remember the last time

53
00:03:13,960 --> 00:03:14,680
I was in the Wolong Valley

54
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:16,319
when I fought 300 giants.

55
00:03:16,879 --> 00:03:17,759
My army was wiped out.

56
00:03:18,479 --> 00:03:19,560
In the end, I was the only one left.

57
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:22,439
I was badly injured

58
00:03:22,439 --> 00:03:23,560
and my hands were dislocated.

59
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:25,120
In the end,

60
00:03:25,599 --> 00:03:26,759
I still managed to survive alone.

61
00:03:27,039 --> 00:03:28,199
I know you're capable.

62
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:30,400
You survived alone

63
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,479
in the wilderness.

64
00:03:31,719 --> 00:03:34,039
He used the beast's strength to reset his hands,

65
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:36,280
and rushed for seven days and nights

66
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:37,280
to reach the enemy camp.

67
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,680
Finally, he killed the enemy leader

68
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:41,319
with his own hands, despite his injuries.

69
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:44,960
How do you know that?

70
00:03:46,319 --> 00:03:47,360
I've read

71
00:03:47,919 --> 00:03:48,680
the Galaxy Chronicle.

72
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:53,400
Do you

73
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:55,400
have an older brother?

74
00:03:57,080 --> 00:03:58,120
His name is Xu Mengxi.

75
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:03,479
Does he have another name

76
00:04:03,599 --> 00:04:04,360
called Wei'an?

77
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:07,479
Wei'an is Xu Mengxi.

78
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:09,360
Xu Mengxi

79
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:10,960
is my author, right?

80
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:12,639
Who told you that?

81
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:15,759
Don't underestimate my detective skills.

82
00:04:16,759 --> 00:04:18,399
Now I just hope you can tell me

83
00:04:19,079 --> 00:04:19,720
where he is.

84
00:04:20,360 --> 00:04:21,839
It's very important to me.

85
00:04:22,720 --> 00:04:23,079
I don't want to say.

86
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:25,720
Uh...

87
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:29,079
Are you not taking advantage of my kindness?

88
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:41,879
I didn't see it.

89
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,399
I saw nothing.

90
00:04:51,399 --> 00:04:52,879
I'll find a way to make you say it.

91
00:04:53,199 --> 00:04:54,000
Just you wait.

92
00:05:16,279 --> 00:05:17,920
I didn't expect this path

93
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:19,720
to be the longest I've ever walked.

94
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:57,199
Mr. Xu,

95
00:05:57,879 --> 00:05:59,839
I know you're a man of integrity.

96
00:06:01,199 --> 00:06:02,920
We've been together for days,

97
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:04,120
and I know

98
00:06:04,519 --> 00:06:05,680
you won't make it hard for me.

99
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:07,439
What conditions do you want?

100
00:06:09,759 --> 00:06:10,920
Just name it.

101
00:06:12,879 --> 00:06:13,519
Wait,

102
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:15,839
where did you learn all this?

103
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:17,199
Short video?

104
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:19,360
Or some unreliable guy?

105
00:06:19,759 --> 00:06:20,920
What are his weaknesses?

106
00:06:21,079 --> 00:06:21,839
I don't know.

107
00:06:22,439 --> 00:06:23,279
But I know

108
00:06:23,639 --> 00:06:25,439
what weaknesses men have.

109
00:06:36,079 --> 00:06:37,120
Hmm.

110
00:06:42,279 --> 00:06:43,240
Blue said

111
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,600
there are a hundred ways to make men obedient.

112
00:06:45,879 --> 00:06:47,079
This is the first way.

113
00:06:47,519 --> 00:06:48,639
It almost took half my life.

114
00:06:54,519 --> 00:06:55,959
Is it useful or not?

115
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:15,959
It's useful.

116
00:08:03,399 --> 00:08:03,800
Yes.

117
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:10,759
I don't eat.

118
00:08:11,399 --> 00:08:12,439
You saw it just now.

119
00:08:13,399 --> 00:08:14,439
It's not that I don't want to help you.

120
00:08:15,439 --> 00:08:17,240
I really can't contact Xu Mengxi.

121
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:28,000
The wind is gentle and humid,

122
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:29,079
with the fragrance of flowers.

123
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:30,839
Too small.

124
00:08:31,399 --> 00:08:32,919
Not like the wind in Qingyun.

125
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:34,519
Cold.

126
00:08:34,879 --> 00:08:35,559
Strong.

127
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:38,039
It passes through when you run.

128
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,840
So free and happy.

129
00:08:42,799 --> 00:08:44,279
Do you really want to go back to Qingyun?
